ingredientsDesc:
Anti-IGFBP-3-Coated Microtitration Strips: One stripholder containing 96 microtitration wells coated with goat anti-IGFBP-3 polyclonal antibody.
IGFBP-3 Standard A/Sample Diluent: containing 0 ng/ml IGFBP-3 in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
IGFBP-3 Standard B-F: Lyophilized.
IGFBP-3 Controls: Lyophilized.
IGFBP-3 Assay Buffer: containing a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
IGFBP-3 Antibody-Enzyme Conjugate Concentrate: containing goat anti-IGFBP-3 polyclonal antibody conjugated to the enzyme horseradish peroxidase in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
TMB Chromogen Solution: containing a solution of tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) in citrate buffer with hydrogen peroxide.
Wash Concentrate: containing buffered saline with a nonionic detergent.
Stopping Solution: containing 0.2 M sulfuric acid.
